name: Kugisaki Nobara Character LoRA
description:
Kugisaki Nobara Character LoRA

If you enjoy my models and want to support me you could buy me a coffee!

This LoRA mimics the character Nobara Kugisaki from Jujutsu Kaisen. If you're gonna use this embedding I recommend adding long hair to your negative prompts for satisfactory results.

The example images were created varying weights and models but feel free to experiment on your own. I tried briefly to mix it with a couple of different embeddings and it gave back decent results but you might find a better way to mix them (changing different weights etc.).

To change the weight just change the '1' in this prompt: <lora:kugisaki-Nobara-LoRA:1>.

I'd love to see the art you guys make with it so feel free to add them in comments.

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default it's :1 which is usually too high)
